        "TileImage": "$($repository e8947a1c-f276-4471-b708-4afba69f4cad).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47. There is an identity sale going on tonight at a hotel in Bangkok. One of these stolen identities is our client, and he wants to eliminate the buyer and seller before it&apos;s too late. However, right now it looks good for us because the targets are apparently unsure where to find each other, so you have plenty of time to come up with something. I would recommend the sniper rifle 47, and as always. good hunting.",
